OL,3,CDevolution for Lancashire: Evolution,
OL,4,Cnot revolution
OL,6,FIt has been eight years in the making.
OL,7,FSince 2015, the 15 individual councils
OL,8,Facross Lancashire have been working
OL,9,Ftowards securing a devolution deal.
OL,11,FFinally, the county looks to have got
OL,12,Fone. But what does it actually mean
OL,13,Fand why is it controversial?
OL,15,FAt its simplest, devolution is the
OL,16,Ftransfer of power from central
OL,17,Fgovernment in Westminster to regions.
OL,18,FIt gives politicians in those places
OL,19,Fmore decision-making responsibility
OL,20,Fand funding.
